OL,3,CWhat do newly released state papers
OL,4,Creveal?
OL,6,FWhen the newly-established Northern
OL,7,FIreland Executive with fully devolved
OL,8,Fpowers reconvened after Christmas, a
OL,9,Frow over flags began to brew.
OL,11,FDeclassified papers include a letter
OL,12,Ffrom then Department for Social
OL,13,FDevelopment minister, Nigel Dodds,
OL,14,Fwhich stated: "I wish to register in
OL,15,Fthe strongest terms possible my
OL,16,Fopposition to any Minister who refuses
OL,17,Fto abide by the Schedule for Days for
OL,18,FHoisting Flags on Government buildings
OL,19,F... This is clearly intended to apply
OL,20,Fon a UK-wide basis."
