OL,4,Creveal?
OL,6,FDuring the first year of direct rule,
OL,7,Fa number of files at the Public
OL,8,FRecords Office in Belfast show plans
OL,9,Ffor the potential introduction of
OL,10,Fwater charges by the Labour government
OL,12,FHistorian Dr Peter McLoughlin said:
OL,13,F"You had British ministers implying
OL,14,Fthat they would bring in water charges
OL,15,Fand therefore a greater cost for
OL,16,Fvoters in Northern Ireland unless the
OL,17,FDUP and Sinn Fein came together.
