OL,4,Creveal?
OL,6,F"There was lots of other issues,
OL,7,Fpolicing and everything that went into
OL,8,Fthe St Andrew's Agreement but water
OL,9,Fcharges was one more thing to try and
OL,10,Fpush voters to push the people that
OL,11,Frepresented them to finally come
OL,12,Ftogether as Sinn Fein and the DUP did."
OL,14,FWhile some issues, like water charges,
OL,15,Fhave not been resolved in more than 20
OL,16,Fyears, there has been progress on
OL,17,Fothers, like Irish language.
