OL,3,CWhat do newly released state papers
OL,4,Creveal?
OL,6,FIn 2004, state papers showed a warning
OL,7,Ffrom judges over the demands caused by
OL,8,Fthe use of Irish language in courts
OL,9,Fstating that this would have the
OL,10,Fpotential to "undermine public
OL,11,Fconfidence" in the justice system.
OL,13,FIn 2020, proposals which would allow
OL,14,Fthe use of Irish in courts were
OL,15,Fincluded in the New Decade New
OL,16,FApproach deal
OL,18,F"Earlier this year legislation was
OL,19,Fbrought in by the Northern Ireland
OL,20,FMinister to say that that would be
OL,21,Fallowed.
